data.description: 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath condo located in North Oaks community. Condo is an end unit with private entry. Downstairs has living room with fire place, dining room, powder room, kitchen with granite counter tops and all new stainless steel appliances. Laminate Wood flooring throughout entire first floor. Access to private spacious patio from unit. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and laundry area with Unit has attached 2 car garage with storage racks and a water softener installed. Community includes pool and spa access, and is within minutes from the 215 and 15 freeways, Super Target and Costco location on Clinton Keith. Assigned to excellent schools in the Murrieta Valley Unified School District.
